---
title: "invalidateOrders (GPV2CompatibleAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_role: require ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE
    q_check_role --> q_loop: access granted
    q_loop --> q_invalidate: i < orderUids.length
    q_loop --> [*]: i >= orderUids.length
    q_invalidate --> q_loop: i_gpV2Settlement.invalidateOrder(orderUids[i])

    note right of q_invalidate
        INV-001: Only ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE can invalidate CowProtocol orders
        INV-002: Delegates to GPv2Settlement contract for order invalidation
    end note
